{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/FirstTitle_EN.png?t=1732669889\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wardens Rising is a one-of-a-kind, action-packed game of heroism, strategy, and epic battles blending high-octane PvE coop ARPG shooter action and MOBA-like base defense strategy for an experience like no other!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an exhilarating campaign against a relentless interdimensional threat. Your mission is to protect vital energy cores from massive invasions and defeat mighty bosses to save humanity and attain everlasting glory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/build_defenses.gif?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan your strategy and build defenses before each battle. Over time you will unlock new defensive technology like towers, traps, portals, walls, and more to use in your next battle.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/defeat_invasions.gif?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To become an elite defender of mankind you must be smart and fight hard to defeat wave after wave of enemy invaders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/choose_a_warden.gif?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from 5 unique heroes to level up and customize with new gear and perks as you progress. Choose a SPEC companion to aid you in battle with their unique abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/campaing_+_mission.gif?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat invasion waves on all 24 campaign maps and overcome challenging boss fights. Elite defenders of humanity can also take on 12 challenging mission-mode maps with new invasions every time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/coop_or_solo.gif?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Allow others to join the fight in your campaign or connect with up to 4 other players for insane large-scale battles in the game\u2019s endlessly replayable mission mode.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Do you have what it takes to become a legendary Warden?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/Steam_Title_7.png?t=1732669889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1055560/extras/Steam_Title_Controller_ENG.png?t=1732669889\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optimized for the controller but offers mouse/keyboard controls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play Solo or Coop with up to 4 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from 5 Unique Wardens to level up and customize with gear, talents, and perks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">25+ tactical items used to compliment your strategy and play style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 SPEC companions, each with unique abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15+ upgradeable defense structures like towers, traps, portals, and walls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24+ campaign maps, 4 bosses, and 12 mission mode maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ tactical items and perks to customize and improve your hero.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12 up-to-4-player mission mode maps.</p></li></ul>","bac